SAY NAME1 ~Smite Evil~ // unidentified name for items OR spell name
SAY NAME2 ~Identified Name~ // identified name for items; not used for spells
SAY UNIDENTIFIED_DESC ~With the Smite ability, the caster gains the ability to strike a mighty blow, knocking an opponent back for a considerable distance and stunning the opponent for 1 round. All attacks made in the first round are critical hits. The ability lasts for 2 rounds.~ // unidentified description for items, spell description for spells
SAY DESC ~Identified Description~ // identified description for items, unused for spells

