SAY UNIDENTIFIED_DESC ~This is the special ability that Corellon gives to His elven paladins. No other class has access to this spell, that gives these temporary bonuses: +1 to all saves, +1 Thac0, +1/2 attack per round, +50% resistance to physical damage, +4 AC and immunity to level drain.~ // unidentified description for items, spell description for spells
