SAY NAME2 ~Identified Name~ // identified name for items; not used for spells
SAY UNIDENTIFIED_DESC ~When casting this spell, and laying his hand upon a creature, the caster causes wounds and other injuries to the creature's body to be healed. The priest can restore 3d8 + 1/level points of damage sustained by the target creature (up to a maximum of 3d8+15). This healing cannot affect creatures without corporeal bodies, nor can it cure wounds of creatures not living or of extraplanar origin.~ // unidentified description for items, spell description for spells
