SAY NAME2 ~Identified Name~ // identified name for items; not used for spells
SAY UNIDENTIFIED_DESC ~This spell creates waves of positive energy that sweep outwards from the caster. This wave disrupts any undead that attempt to attack the caster, pushing them away from the caster for several seconds. There is one wave each round for the duration of the spell. All undead are affected, without a saving throw.~ // unidentified description for items, spell description for spells
